16:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda pensiya yoshi: erkaklar — 60 yosh, ayollar — 55 yosh. 2026-yil iyunidan boshlab 20 yil va undan ko'p ish stajiga ega ayollar 1 yil erta — 54 yoshda pensiyaga chiqish huquqiga ega bo'ladi. Yoshi bo'yicha to'liq pensiya olish uchun minimal ish staji zarur: erkaklar uchun 25 yil va ayollar uchun 20 yil. Staj yetarli bo'lmaganda (lekin 7 yildan kam bo'lmasa) mutanosib miqdorda pensiya tayinlanadi. 2026-yil 1-yanvardan davlat ijtimoiy sug'urta to'g'risidagi №1101-son Qonun kuchga kirdi, u ijtimoiy to'lovlar tizimini, jumladan pensiya ta'minotini isloh qiladi. Minimal pensiya taxminan 1 "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/bhm","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"BHK"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" (412 000 so'm) ni tashkil etadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Pensiya hisoblash formulasi: Pensiya = Eng yaxshi ketma-ket 5 yildagi o'rtacha ish haqi × (55% + minimaldan ortiq har yil staj uchun 1%). Maksimal miqdor — o'rtacha ish haqining 75%. 25 yil stajda: 55% + 0% = 55%. 35 yil stajda: 55% + 10% = 65%. 45 yil stajda: 55% + 20% = 75% (maksimum). O'rtacha ish haqi minimal ish haqi o'sishini hisobga olgan holda indeksatsiya qilinadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"2023-yildan O'zbekistonda jamg'arma pensiya tizimi — individual jamg'arma pensiya hisobvarag'i ("}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/ish-haqi","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"IJPH"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":") amal qilmoqda. Majburiy to'lov hisoblangan ish haqining 0,1% ni tashkil etadi va ish beruvchi tomonidan ushlab qolinadi. Jamg'armalar xodimning shaxsiy mulki, meros qilib qoldiriladi va tortib olinishi mumkin emas. Pensiyaga chiqqanda yig'ilgan summa pensionerning tanloviga ko'ra bir martalik yoki bo'lib to'lanadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Bir qator toifalar uchun muddatidan oldingi pensiya nazarda tutilgan: zararli ishlab chiqarish xodimlari (1 va 2-ro'yxatlar), pedagoglar (25 yil stajda), tibbiyot xodimlari (25-30 yil stajda), ko'p bolali onalar (5+ bola — 50 yoshdan). Harbiylar va kuch tuzilmalari xodimlari xizmat muddati bo'yicha (20 yil) pensiyaga chiqadilar. Pensiyalar har yili yashash minimumi o'sishiga muvofiq indeksatsiya qilinadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":["$L1b","$L1c","$L1d"]}]]}]]}],"$L1e","$L1f","$L20"]}]
